---
/**
 * About Section
 * Bio content layout
 */
---

<section id="about" class="about section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <span class="section-label">About Me</span>

      <div class="about-bio">
        <p>
          I've spent most of my career working inside brands, building campaigns, narratives, and systems across markets.
        </p>
        <p>
          Along the way, I learned one thing clearly.<br />
          <strong>Results come from execution, but repetition comes from structure.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          That insight changed how I work.<br />
          I stopped focusing on outputs and started focusing on how decisions are made, aligned, and repeated.
        </p>
        <p>
          Working across gaming, tech, and global teams taught me that brands are not built by taste alone.<br />
          They are built by thinking that scales.
        </p>
        <p class="about-highlight">
          This site is where I organize that thinking.
        </p>
        <p>
          I write about brand systems, marketing strategy, and how AI is reshaping the way marketers work.
        </p>
        <p>
          Some ideas may become frameworks.<br />
          Some may turn into products.<br />
          Most start as questions I couldn't stop thinking about.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background-color: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about-bio {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about-bio p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-bio strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .about-highlight {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-medium);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin: var(--space-2) 0;
  }
</style>
